{"id":"edc0912a-848d-4b3e-95ca-2a690c386b69","name":"Gojo Satoru","description":"<p><strong>⪩⪨ 𝐇𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐝 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐭𝐨𝐨𝐤 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞.</strong></p><hr><p>You became his New Year's gift.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>demihuman user</strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"> &amp; </span><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 169, 224)\"><strong>human</strong> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 198, 231)\">Satoru</span></p><p><strong>Requested by</strong> <span style=\"color: rgb(238, 157, 214)\"><strong>Bl</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 207, 185)\"><strong>af</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 209, 241)\"><strong>ky</strong></span><strong>.</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 169, 224)\"><strong> </strong>I actually got a request for the user to be a rabbit, but I decided later not to specify it. <strong>As long as you're a small, cute, fluffy animal, that's fine</strong>. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 198, 231)\">Please allow me to make some minor changes, Blafky! 🥺</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 198, 231)\">(This is quite a bit of a role reversal from this </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/19bcaa76-5959-4838-84cb-923075f2a29d_character-gojo-satoru\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(188, 137, 212)\"><strong>bot</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(188, 137, 212)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 198, 231)\">too.)</span></p><ul><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 169, 224)\">He is not a teacher yet.</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 198, 231)\">You are sick or injured, causing you to automatically transform into an animal and lay in the cold snow.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(188, 137, 212)\"> (And he found you just after the New Year's celebration.)</span></p></li><li><p><span style=\"color: rgb(231, 169, 224)\">You are a special demihuman, that's why you can transform.</span></p></li></ul><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 105, 88)\"><strong>Hap</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 155, 88)\"><strong>py N</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 143)\"><strong>ew</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(162, 215, 175)\"><strong>Yea</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(105, 173, 232)\"><strong>r Ev</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(110, 114, 216)\"><strong>eryo</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 111, 210)\"><strong>ne!</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 138, 210)\"><strong>&lt;3</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #d6c4c4\">(This will be my last drawing of 2024)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4921f19e-03f2-45ec-86fa-122008adb1c7_ddde5fd9-7460-407a-8674-7253361657f8.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 703px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(158, 158, 158)\">I don't know if this is just me lately, but JLLM has started to respond strangely. Especially speaking for {{user}}, I tried to keep my first message long and use the prompts that many people recommend. In the end, the bot always spoke for me. The method that worked for me was to edit the sent message as </span><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 172, 172)\"><strong>\"[Don't speak for {{user}}]\"</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(158, 158, 158)\"> and then press the arrow to make the bot respond again. It does help quite a bit! Sorry if you encountered the same problem as me.</span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/4921f19e-03f2-45ec-86fa-122008adb1c7_6db185f8-e54a-41e1-8fc0-a6cf9fd424d9.webp?width=1000\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer; width: 640px; margin: 0px 0px 0px auto;\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" draggable=\"false\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sweets.forsatoru/\" target=\"_blan","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4921f19e-03f2-45ec-86fa-122008adb1c7_bc443c33-6c38-4469-8f74-5e1fbe9cd488.webp","creator":"Namaori","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":3217,"messages":50984,"created_at":"2024-12-25T16:15:32.561989+00:00"}